bilingual.source: This moisturizing mask helps to rejuvenate tired skin.
bilingual.target: 这款保湿面膜有助于恢复疲劳的皮肤。

bilingual.source: Sleep can help the body repair its tired tissue (组织).
bilingual.target: 睡眠可以帮助身体修复疲劳的组织。

bilingual.source: There is a tired woman in sidestep.
bilingual.target: 台阶上有一个疲劳的妇女.

bilingual.source: With my restless heart and my tired bones.
bilingual.target: 得不到安宁的心呀,疲劳的筋骨呀.

bilingual.source: Comrade Wang told me that was why he was not a little tired.
bilingual.target: 王同志告诉我那就是为什么他非常疲劳的原因。

bilingual.source: A: As beginners, you need to start slowly, or you'll get tired soon.
bilingual.target: 刚开始，你得慢慢来，不然你很容易就会疲劳的。

bilingual.source: Comrade Wang told me that that was why he was not a little tired.
bilingual.target: 王同志告诉我那就是为什么他非常疲劳的原因。

bilingual.source: With a good night’s sleep, tired eyes should quickly return to normal.
bilingual.target: 只需要晚上睡个好觉，疲劳的眼睛很快就恢复正常了。

bilingual.source: It can calm down the tired nerve and make up the storage of the energy your body need.
bilingual.target: 这个具有恢复功效的体式，能平静疲劳的神经和重新补足身体能量的储备。

bilingual.source: Seaweed & aloe vera are highly effective ingredients for soothing sore, tired eyes.
bilingual.target: 即：“海藻芦荟对于于舒缓酸痛、疲劳的眼部具备着高效的成分。

list.abstract: tired（英 [ˈtaɪəd]，美 [ˈtaɪərd]），英语单词，形容词，意思为疲倦的；疲劳的；累的。短语搭配有get tired（累了）。例句为“Finish them before they get tired.（在他们累之前完成这些活儿。）” tired相关近义词有worn、harassed，相关反义词有refreshed、interested等。
tired是许怀欣演唱的国语歌曲，收录在其专辑《天下不乱》

yingyinNormal.en: How do you feel? Tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 感觉怎么样？很累。

yingyinNormal.en: How do you feel? I'm tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在感觉如何？累啊。

yingyinNormal.en: Now you must be tired. Hungry? Uh-huh.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们一定又累又饿吧? 是啊。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm a bit tired. It's been a long day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我有点困了，累了一天了。

yingyinNormal.en: Not funny. She's tired, that was funny.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不好笑。她太累了，你说得很好笑。

yingyinNormal.en: My head hurts and I'm more tired than ever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的头好疼，我此生第一次这么累。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I guess Walter got tired of buying it.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看来沃尔特已经厌倦了。

yingyinNormal.en: That's not why you're tired. Excuse me? You are not tired because of work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那不是你累了的原因。你说什么？你不是因为工作感到疲惫。

yingyinNormal.en: Seemed to do the trick. And you thought your troubles were over. I was tired. Tired of the mess of it all.
yingyinNormal.zh: 似乎挺成功。你以为你的麻烦结束了。我累了。厌倦了这一切麻烦。

yingyinNormal.en: I know, I know. I'm just so tired of missing him. I'm tired of wondering why hasn't he called. Why hasn't he called.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道，我只是不想再这么想他，不愿再去想他为何不打来？他为何都没打来？

yingyinNormal.en: That was eight. I'm a bit tired. I'll do the rest later.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你只转了八个。我感觉有点累了。剩下的我一会再转吧。

yingyinNormal.en: What is all of this? I got it. Good. Tired. Four o'clock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是怎么回事？我来搞定。很好，累，四点。

yingyinNormal.en: But we want to ride our own bicycles. George is a bit too little. His legs will get very tired. But I am a big girl, I won't get tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是我们想骑我们自己的自行车。乔治现在还太小了，那样他会非常累的。但是我已经长大了，我想我肯定不会累。

yingyinNormal.en: So they got divorced and Dale moved in. Tired. Go to sleep.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以他们离婚了，然后戴尔就搬了进来。我累了，去睡吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig. Oh, sorry. I'm a bit tired. It's been a long day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸！抱歉，我有点困了，累了一天了。

yingyinNormal.en: Daddy Pig! Oh, sorry. I'm a bit tired. It's been a long day.
yingyinNormal.zh: 猪爸爸！哦，对不起，我有点累了。今天真的很长。

yingyinNormal.en: At 3:00 in the afternoon? I was tired. And no one saw you there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那天下午三点？我很累。没人看见你在那儿。

yingyinNormal.en: I want death. Get off my case, Mathilda. I'm tired of your games.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我选择死亡，玛蒂尔达，放过我吧，我对你的游戏已经感到厌倦了。

yingyinNormal.en: Why would we go back? Because we're struggling. Because I'm tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们为什么要回去呢？因为我们在挣扎，因为我累了。

yingyinNormal.en: You took off your pants and climbed under the sheets. I was tired.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你脱了裤子钻进被子里。我累了。

examination_example.sentence: I can focus on a mental task for long periods without feeling <highlight>tired</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我可以长时间专注于一项心理作业而不感到疲劳。

examination_example.sentence: When people imagine themselves as advisers and imagine their own choices as belonging to someone else, they feel less <highlight>tired</highlight>.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当人们将自己想象成顾问，或想象到自己为他人做选择时，他们就不会那么疲惫。

examination_example.sentence: There we all were <highlight>tired</highlight> and hungry, and then we made the great discovery.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们都很疲惫饥饿，然后我们有了重大发。

examination_example.sentence: Working parents say they feel stressed, <highlight>tired</highlight>, rushed and short on quality time with their children, friends and partners.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 有工作的父母表示，他们感到压力大、累、匆忙，缺少与孩子、朋友和伴侣在一起的宝贵时间。

sense_info_list.zh: 老套乏味的; 令人生厌的

examination_example.sentence: Humans would be <highlight>tired</highlight> of communicating with one another.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人类厌倦了彼此之间的交流。

examination_example.sentence: I never worry about what I'm wearing in the morning, even if I do get a bit <highlight>tired</highlight> of just wearing the same classic pieces.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我从不担心我早上穿什么，即使我确实有点厌倦只穿同样的经典服装。

examination_example.sentence: Once it's fully developed, AI will become <highlight>tired</highlight> of trying to communicate with humans as we would be much slower thinkers in comparison.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 人工智能一旦完全成熟，它就会厌倦尝试与人类交流，因为相比之下，人类的思维速度要慢得多。

examination_example.sentence: When people experience decision fatigue-when they are <highlight>tired</highlight> of making choices-they have a tendency to choose to go with status quo (现状).
examination_example.sentence_trans: 当人们感到决策疲劳时，厌倦做出选择时，他们倾向于选择符合现状的状态。
